1
00:00:15,836 --> 00:00:20,136
If anyone knew that you were homosexual, it would be ruined

2
00:00:20,137 --> 00:00:23,536
But you're my brother and you acted like someone else

3
00:00:23,736 --> 00:00:38,536
just because I'm not a real man.
So you would understand how I feel.

4
00:00:38,536 --> 00:00:41,336
What're you doing? You're acting as the lead actress of the live performance

5
00:00:41,337 --> 00:00:43,536
Can you perform for me? I want to watch you.

6
00:00:43,836 --> 00:00:46,536
Why did you wrap your head with a scarf like that? Where did you get it?

7
00:00:46,636 --> 00:00:49,336
This is bad. Tian is about to be like Mr.Zhang.

8
00:00:49,536 --> 00:00:51,936
You can't do this again, you hear me?

9
00:00:52,336 --> 00:00:54,136
Don't

10
00:00:55,136 --> 00:00:55,836
Burn it.

11
00:00:56,336 --> 00:00:58,736
Everyone said that it was a secret.

12
00:00:58,737 --> 00:01:00,136
A stick and a piece of fabric?

13
00:01:00,137 --> 00:01:02,336
It must be something important and wicked for sure.

14
00:01:02,337 --> 00:01:03,736
What're you hiding? Let me see.

15
00:01:03,737 --> 00:01:04,736
I won't.

16
00:01:04,737 --> 00:01:06,136
Please / Give it to me.

17
00:01:06,137 --> 00:01:08,136
You can't mess with Tian again.
Ouch!

18
00:01:08,137 --> 00:01:10,436
You should focus only raising a good son.

19
00:01:10,536 --> 00:01:13,936
When I forbid you and you didn't listen to me, it will be a punishment.

20
00:01:13,937 --> 00:01:18,136
I told you that you'd be in trouble if someone knew about it

21
00:01:18,536 --> 00:01:19,136
Madame!

22
00:03:21,536 --> 00:03:28,136
Tian! Tian.

23
00:03:45,336 --> 00:03:46,336
Where're Tian?

24
00:04:08,536 --> 00:04:09,536
Tian!

25
00:04:17,136 --> 00:04:19,136
There're some situations.

26
00:04:23,936 --> 00:04:26,336
You accused me of cheating?

27
00:04:27,136 --> 00:04:29,536
You! Ouch!

28
00:04:31,736 --> 00:04:32,536
I cheated?/Stop.

29
00:04:36,136 --> 00:04:37,136
What's going on?

30
00:04:38,536 --> 00:04:39,736
Why were you two in a fight like this?

31
00:04:41,136 --> 00:04:43,836
Dong frauded me.

32
00:04:44,136 --> 00:04:46,136
You accepted money from me already.

33
00:04:46,336 --> 00:04:50,536
Don't listen to him.

34
00:04:51,136 --> 00:04:53,136
He could spend it on liquor or something else.

35
00:04:53,336 --> 00:04:54,736
You wanted to reimburse more?

36
00:04:56,136 --> 00:04:58,936
That's not true. Dong is a cheater.

37
00:04:59,336 --> 00:05:02,736
I'll use that money to cure my mother. She is sick.

38
00:05:03,336 --> 00:05:05,336
Please, bring me justice.

39
00:05:16,536 --> 00:05:18,736
Take this and get up.

40
00:05:26,736 --> 00:05:30,536
I heard noises, what's going on?

41
00:05:31,136 --> 00:05:33,336
They fought because of wages.

42
00:05:35,136 --> 00:05:37,136
Dong said that he already paid Zhao.

43
00:05:37,336 --> 00:05:39,136
But Zhao said that he didn't get money from Dong.

44
00:05:46,536 --> 00:05:47,536
What about that money?

45
00:05:49,136 --> 00:05:50,736
It's mine.

46
00:05:51,536 --> 00:05:55,536
Zhao said that he'd use it to heal his sick mother. So I gave it to him.

47
00:05:56,336 --> 00:05:58,136
How could you let this happen?

48
00:05:59,336 --> 00:06:02,736
Did you have any proof that you paid him?

49
00:06:03,736 --> 00:06:05,536
But I paid him already.

50
00:06:10,136 --> 00:06:11,136
Everybody, listen.

51
00:06:12,836 --> 00:06:16,736
From now on, come to me to get your wages.

52
00:06:17,836 --> 00:06:20,536
I'll take care of payment instead of Dong.

53
00:06:20,537 --> 00:06:22,936
So you believed Zhao

54
00:06:23,136 --> 00:06:24,736
and accused me of cheating about wages?

55
00:06:24,737 --> 00:06:25,736
That's enough.

56
00:06:26,836 --> 00:06:29,136
Tian tried to build a system to this.

57
00:06:30,936 --> 00:06:33,136
You should do what he said.

58
00:06:42,936 --> 00:06:44,136
Well done.

59
00:06:45,336 --> 00:06:46,336
Thank you.

60
00:06:55,336 --> 00:06:56,536
Where's my son?

61
00:06:57,736 --> 00:06:59,136
I don't know.

62
00:07:02,536 --> 00:07:04,336
Flowers. / You want some gourd?

63
00:07:04,337 --> 00:07:06,136
You want some flowers?

64
00:07:06,137 --> 00:07:10,136
We have roses, how many'd you like?

65
00:07:10,137 --> 00:07:12,136
Can I have three please? / Sure.

66
00:07:12,137 --> 00:07:15,136
Lotus is pretty too, I'll take two / Sure.

67
00:07:15,137 --> 00:07:16,136
Pandan? / I'll take this one too.

68
00:07:18,136 --> 00:07:18,636
Ouch!

69
00:07:22,936 --> 00:07:24,736
You slapped me?

70
00:07:24,737 --> 00:07:29,136
Help me! Ouch! Help!

71
00:07:37,336 --> 00:07:38,136
Who're you ?

72
00:07:38,536 --> 00:07:41,136
You piece of crap! You hurt women!

73
00:07:43,336 --> 00:07:45,136
You! Ouch!

74
00:07:48,536 --> 00:07:49,336
Yeah?

75
00:07:49,736 --> 00:07:50,236
Hey!

76
00:07:52,736 --> 00:07:55,136
Ouch!

77
00:07:55,736 --> 00:07:56,236
Hey!

78
00:08:04,136 --> 00:08:07,136
Hey! / Ouch!

79
00:08:07,536 --> 00:08:10,136
Hey! / Water!

80
00:08:10,137 --> 00:08:14,136
Hey! / What?

81
00:08:15,136 --> 00:08:16,536
You're asking for it

82
00:08:18,836 --> 00:08:22,536
Here. Keep it.

83
00:08:27,536 --> 00:08:29,436
You want these? / Ouch!

84
00:08:34,136 --> 00:08:36,136
You're so good at this.

85
00:09:01,536 --> 00:09:04,636
Where's Yang?

86
00:09:05,136 --> 00:09:08,136
I've been waiting for him to join the table and he didn't show up.

87
00:09:08,536 --> 00:09:10,136
You should teach him about this.

88
00:09:12,136 --> 00:09:13,136
Yes, sir.

89
00:09:14,336 --> 00:09:17,836
He must be out and about like he used to.

90
00:09:18,336 --> 00:09:21,436
If you're hungry, then we should start.

91
00:09:21,736 --> 00:09:24,436
Nope. I'll wait for him.

92
00:09:25,136 --> 00:09:26,436
I want to see his face

93
00:09:26,636 --> 00:09:30,536
when he comes back and sees that everyone is waiting for him.

94
00:09:31,136 --> 00:09:34,136
I hope that he didn't go out and get in a fight with anyone.

95
00:09:34,336 --> 00:09:36,536
I'm so sick of him already.

96
00:09:55,536 --> 00:09:58,536
They're all here?

97
00:10:07,136 --> 00:10:11,336
Yang? Everyone is waiting for you.

98
00:10:14,836 --> 00:10:16,136
Nuan.

99
00:10:17,936 --> 00:10:18,736
Let's go.

100
00:10:34,336 --> 00:10:36,436
I knew it.

101
00:10:37,536 --> 00:10:41,136
Whom were you in a fight with? There're bruises.

102
00:10:41,137 --> 00:10:43,136
Don't scold him. Please listen to him.

103
00:10:43,137 --> 00:10:46,136
I won't. Why would I ?

104
00:10:46,137 --> 00:10:49,536
We can see evidence on his face. He was in a fight with someone

105
00:10:50,136 --> 00:10:51,536
You're useless.

106
00:10:53,136 --> 00:10:57,536
You didn't pay attention in school and you only focused on shooting and fishing.

107
00:10:58,136 --> 00:11:00,536
Don't ever think about comparing yourself to Tian.

108
00:11:01,136 --> 00:11:04,636
You can't even compare yourself to the pier's workers.

109
00:11:06,536 --> 00:11:07,936
Listen to me.

110
00:11:07,937 --> 00:11:12,136
You can't go out and get in a fight with anyone anymore.

111
00:11:12,536 --> 00:11:15,136
You need to stay home, you hear me?

112
00:11:17,836 --> 00:11:21,536
I think we should start eating.

113
00:11:21,736 --> 00:11:25,336
Then we can start talking about something else. Go sit with me.

114
00:11:26,336 --> 00:11:27,136
Never mind.

115
00:11:28,136 --> 00:11:32,736
I think I should go. If I stayed here, dad wouldn't be able to eat.

116
00:11:33,536 --> 00:11:37,936
And I want to think about working.

117
00:11:38,136 --> 00:11:44,436
I'm afraid that if I help you with work,
the successful business could be a failure. I should go.

118
00:11:47,136 --> 00:11:48,436
Yang? / Don't

119
00:11:48,836 --> 00:11:52,536
Let him go. Let him starve to death.

120
00:11:53,136 --> 00:11:56,436
He's so cocky. Let's eat.

121
00:12:21,936 --> 00:12:25,736
It smells so good.

122
00:12:26,836 --> 00:12:28,536
I'm sorry.

123
00:12:29,136 --> 00:12:31,536
You have to cook for me again. I'm sorry about that.

124
00:12:31,736 --> 00:12:34,336
Well, you shouldn't argue with your dad too often.

125
00:12:36,336 --> 00:12:37,336
Can I help?

126
00:12:38,736 --> 00:12:41,136
I'm almost done.

127
00:12:44,536 --> 00:12:48,136
I knew that you would ask Bua to feed you.

128
00:12:56,336 --> 00:12:58,136
What's wrong with your face?

129
00:12:59,536 --> 00:13:01,636
Answer me nicely.

130
00:13:02,536 --> 00:13:04,536
I got in a fight with Japanese soldiers.

131
00:13:05,336 --> 00:13:08,136
I saw them hurting a woman and I couldn't help it.

132
00:13:08,336 --> 00:13:09,936
So I taught them a lesson or two.

133
00:13:10,136 --> 00:13:11,736
Why didn't you tell dad about this?

134
00:13:12,536 --> 00:13:15,536
If he knew the real reason, he wouldn't have scolded you like that.

135
00:13:17,136 --> 00:13:18,736
What about work?

136
00:13:19,136 --> 00:13:23,336
You know that I've never wanted to work since the beginning.

137
00:13:23,536 --> 00:13:26,136
We were raised to hate each other.

138
00:13:26,836 --> 00:13:30,336
My mom raised me to hate you and your mom was no different.

139
00:13:30,536 --> 00:13:31,936
If I worked there,

140
00:13:31,937 --> 00:13:34,536
my mom would pressure me to compete with you.

141
00:13:34,936 --> 00:13:37,336
If I agreed with mom,

142
00:13:37,337 --> 00:13:40,636
and crossed the line, you could hate me too.

143
00:13:40,936 --> 00:13:44,536
But I want you to learn about this job from dad very soon.

144
00:13:45,736 --> 00:13:47,736
If I couldn't be working here,

145
00:13:48,136 --> 00:13:51,736
you would be the one to help him with everything.

146
00:13:52,536 --> 00:13:53,336
You know that?

147
00:13:54,636 --> 00:13:57,336
You should be the one taking care of the business.

148
00:13:57,836 --> 00:14:00,536
You can do anything.

149
00:14:00,936 --> 00:14:06,336
You're a kind-hearted person. The workers love you. You're so perfect.

150
00:14:09,136 --> 00:14:11,136
Nobody is perfect.

151
00:14:12,336 --> 00:14:15,136
I could have something bad hidden from everyone.

152
00:14:18,336 --> 00:14:22,136
I don't like to see you like this.

153
00:14:22,536 --> 00:14:26,136
You've always kept your feeling since you were young.

154
00:14:27,336 --> 00:14:29,536
Can I make you feel better?

155
00:14:32,536 --> 00:14:33,936
You can't help me with that.

156
00:14:48,536 --> 00:14:50,736
What about this? Does it help?

157
00:15:01,536 --> 00:15:02,536
I bought it for you.

158
00:15:03,736 --> 00:15:07,136
It will be a Chinese opera performance at the temple in a few days.

159
00:15:07,336 --> 00:15:08,736
I'll take you there.

160
00:15:10,136 --> 00:15:13,736
Good. Since the Japanese soldiers are here for war,

161
00:15:13,936 --> 00:15:15,736
we didn't have a lot of fun events.

162
00:15:17,736 --> 00:15:21,136
But dad didn't let you go outside, what should we do?

163
00:15:22,536 --> 00:15:24,136
I'll take you to sneak out.

164
00:15:24,636 --> 00:15:28,136
We were just kids but I remembered our promises

165
00:15:28,536 --> 00:15:32,136
that I'd take you to watch Chinese opera everywhere.

166
00:15:36,536 --> 00:15:40,336
I'm done. Let's eat.

167
00:15:40,536 --> 00:15:41,336
Yes.

168
00:16:24,136 --> 00:16:28,936
Did Yang eat anything yesterday?

169
00:16:29,636 --> 00:16:31,536
I saw he went to Bua's place.

170
00:16:31,537 --> 00:16:33,136
He could be fed already.

171
00:16:42,336 --> 00:16:43,136
Bua.

172
00:16:44,136 --> 00:16:46,536
You're here? What's going on?

173
00:16:47,136 --> 00:16:49,136
I'd like to talk about Yang.

174
00:16:50,336 --> 00:16:53,136
He asked you to talk to me?

175
00:16:54,136 --> 00:16:57,336
He knows that I love you so he asked for your help.

176
00:16:57,836 --> 00:17:02,136
It's not like that. He's never asked me.

177
00:17:02,536 --> 00:17:04,136
He couldn't asked you directly

178
00:17:04,536 --> 00:17:07,136
but you felt bad for him.

179
00:17:07,536 --> 00:17:10,336
You're too nice to him.

180
00:17:10,536 --> 00:17:13,136
You spoiled him and he could get used to that.

181
00:17:13,536 --> 00:17:15,736
I didn't spoil him.

182
00:17:15,737 --> 00:17:18,536
I just don't judge him like you do.

183
00:17:18,936 --> 00:17:22,736
You judge me too. I scolded him like that

184
00:17:23,536 --> 00:17:25,536
because I didn't want him to go outside.

185
00:17:25,736 --> 00:17:28,136
There are Japanese soldiers everywhere, it's dangerous.

186
00:17:28,137 --> 00:17:29,936
It's not like I hate him or anything.

187
00:17:30,336 --> 00:17:34,136
You love him. Why didn't you talk to him nicely?

188
00:17:34,536 --> 00:17:37,136
If it was Tian who came home late last night,

189
00:17:37,536 --> 00:17:41,536
would you talk to him harshly like you did to Yang?

190
00:17:41,537 --> 00:17:44,736
Yan has been mischievous like this for so many times.

191
00:17:44,836 --> 00:17:47,136
I can't talk to him nicely, I don't want to encourage him.

192
00:17:53,936 --> 00:17:59,136
Mischievous? Or you just don't like the way he talks?

193
00:18:01,136 --> 00:18:03,136
You're lucky

194
00:18:03,336 --> 00:18:06,136
that Tian and Yang love each other.

195
00:18:06,536 --> 00:18:11,136
Otherwise, they would think that you love one more than another.

196
00:18:14,636 --> 00:18:17,136
You're telling me off like this?

197
00:18:31,836 --> 00:18:33,836
What's bothering you?

198
00:18:36,136 --> 00:18:38,136
It's about Tian.

199
00:18:38,536 --> 00:18:41,536
My husband loves and adores him

200
00:18:42,336 --> 00:18:44,336
but I'm still worried.

201
00:18:45,136 --> 00:18:49,336
You shouldn't be worried. Tian is undefeated

202
00:18:49,836 --> 00:18:52,536
because Yang is mischievous and he gets into a fight all the time.

203
00:18:54,136 --> 00:18:55,636
That's what I'm worried.

204
00:18:56,536 --> 00:19:00,136
If Tian starts to be a mischief and getting into a fight like Yang,

205
00:19:00,536 --> 00:19:03,736
I could teach him to behave himself so he could change.

206
00:19:04,736 --> 00:19:08,336
But I can't change who he actually is.

207
00:19:09,636 --> 00:19:12,536
No matter how much Yang makes my husband upset

208
00:19:12,537 --> 00:19:17,136
or furious about him, he's still superior to Tian.

209
00:19:17,536 --> 00:19:19,136
Because Yang is a real man.

210
00:19:19,636 --> 00:19:20,336
Madame!

211
00:19:21,136 --> 00:19:25,136
I don't know if it's my own karma or Zhang's curse

212
00:19:25,336 --> 00:19:27,136
that Tian has been this way.

213
00:19:29,136 --> 00:19:31,536
He will be destroying himself

214
00:19:32,336 --> 00:19:35,136
if my husband or anyone know about this.

215
00:19:37,336 --> 00:19:39,136
How could anyone know about this?

216
00:19:40,136 --> 00:19:46,136
There are only me, you and Tian who know about this.

217
00:19:46,536 --> 00:19:49,936
The secret will continue to be a secret.

218
00:20:13,336 --> 00:20:15,136
You're good at this.

219
00:20:18,336 --> 00:20:21,136
Can you help me?

220
00:20:21,336 --> 00:20:24,536
No one is better at this than Dong.

221
00:20:37,836 --> 00:20:41,736
You brought me this western perfume?

222
00:20:42,136 --> 00:20:45,636
It smells nice and it suits someone pretty like you.

223
00:20:50,736 --> 00:20:52,836
Thank you so much.

224
00:20:53,736 --> 00:20:55,636
You want to watch Chinese opera with me?

225
00:20:57,636 --> 00:21:00,136
I'm not free.

226
00:21:00,336 --> 00:21:04,336
I haven't told you when and you're not free already?

227
00:21:05,736 --> 00:21:09,136
I'm not free because I don't like.

228
00:21:09,536 --> 00:21:12,136
You're asking for it? Come on.

229
00:21:13,836 --> 00:21:16,136
If you don't like the performance, then what do you like?

230
00:21:16,536 --> 00:21:20,536
It's not that she doesn't like the performance, she doesn't like you.

231
00:21:20,736 --> 00:21:21,336
You shut up!

232
00:21:21,337 --> 00:21:24,736
That's right. You should stop dreaming about her already.

233
00:21:24,936 --> 00:21:27,336
Mud is ambitious.

234
00:21:27,636 --> 00:21:30,736
I'm the worker's leader and I'm not good enough for her,

235
00:21:30,936 --> 00:21:32,336
then who is?

236
00:21:48,536 --> 00:21:49,536
What is it?

237
00:21:50,136 --> 00:21:52,136
I saw that you're still up.

238
00:21:54,136 --> 00:21:58,136
I thought that you might be working so I brought you tea.

239
00:22:03,736 --> 00:22:04,736
Thank you.

240
00:22:05,336 --> 00:22:06,536
You're welcome.

241
00:22:08,536 --> 00:22:13,536
My bangle dropped. I'm sorry.

242
00:22:44,336 --> 00:22:46,136
Tian?

243
00:22:49,536 --> 00:22:52,136
What're you doing?

244
00:22:53,736 --> 00:22:55,636
I dropped my bangle.

245
00:22:56,336 --> 00:23:00,336
You scum! You think I don't know your trick?

246
00:23:00,836 --> 00:23:03,336
You're from a lower class and you reach up to someone higher than you.

247
00:23:03,536 --> 00:23:06,136
You should look at yourself.

248
00:23:06,836 --> 00:23:09,736
I think I should tell Madame to fire you.

249
00:23:10,136 --> 00:23:13,436
What's going on? / Madame.

250
00:23:14,136 --> 00:23:19,136
I brought Tian some tea and I dropped my bangle.

251
00:23:19,336 --> 00:23:22,136
Aunt Jia saw me and she misunderstood me.

252
00:23:22,137 --> 00:23:23,536
I didn't misunderstand her.

253
00:23:23,836 --> 00:23:26,536
I could tell that you tried to seduce Tian in just a glance.

254
00:23:35,836 --> 00:23:40,536
You should stay here and take care of Tian.

255
00:23:41,136 --> 00:23:42,136
Mom!

256
00:23:46,136 --> 00:23:49,436
You can take care of him until the next morning.

257
00:23:50,836 --> 00:23:52,136
Let's go.

258
00:23:56,536 --> 00:23:57,336
Madame!

259
00:24:15,136 --> 00:24:18,136
You know that Mud is seducing Tian,

260
00:24:18,137 --> 00:24:20,536
instead of stopping her, why did you let her do that?

261
00:24:22,536 --> 00:24:25,936
It'd be better if she can make Tian become her boyfriend tonight.

262
00:24:26,136 --> 00:24:29,736
Mud is a servant and she's too ambitious.

263
00:24:29,737 --> 00:24:32,736
If Tian falls for her, she could be arrogant and that'd be worse.

264
00:24:33,536 --> 00:24:35,136
I don't care about that.

265
00:24:36,336 --> 00:24:39,336
I just want Tian to change his mind and become a real man

266
00:24:39,337 --> 00:24:41,436
before everything is too late.

267
00:24:46,536 --> 00:24:49,136
You can leave, don't mind my mom.

268
00:24:49,336 --> 00:24:50,136
I can't.

269
00:24:55,836 --> 00:24:58,136
I need to follow her order, strictly.

270
00:24:59,636 --> 00:25:02,136
I'll take care of you until the next morning.

271
00:25:06,936 --> 00:25:08,736
Tian?

272
00:25:09,136 --> 00:25:11,336
Mud!

273
00:25:22,336 --> 00:25:26,636
Why's that? Because I'm just a servant?

274
00:25:27,136 --> 00:25:32,636
You're a woman. You should respect yourself and have dignity.

275
00:25:33,536 --> 00:25:36,136
Don't lower your standard like this.

276
00:25:37,136 --> 00:25:41,536
One more thing, I don't care about your status, whether you're an aristocrat or a servant,

277
00:25:42,536 --> 00:25:44,136
I won't take advantage of you.

278
00:25:45,736 --> 00:25:48,136
Oh my!

279
00:25:48,936 --> 00:25:52,136
Please take advantage of me. I wouldn't mind.

280
00:25:52,137 --> 00:25:52,637
Mud!

281
00:25:53,636 --> 00:25:56,936
Tian!

282
00:25:59,536 --> 00:26:02,936
Why is it so hard to seduce him? I almost got him.

283
00:26:10,536 --> 00:26:14,336
Mom? Why did you tell Mud do this to me?

284
00:26:15,836 --> 00:26:20,336
You're a young man. People at your age want a woman, don't you?

285
00:26:20,536 --> 00:26:22,536
You know that I don't like it.

286
00:26:24,736 --> 00:26:27,936
I can't find the type that you like for you.

287
00:26:32,636 --> 00:26:33,936
Mom?

288
00:26:35,336 --> 00:26:40,136
You've forced me since I was young,

289
00:26:41,136 --> 00:26:44,736
You told me to do this and not to do that.

290
00:26:46,336 --> 00:26:49,136
I've always listened to you.

291
00:26:51,136 --> 00:26:53,336
Because I hope that one day you'll accept me.

292
00:26:54,136 --> 00:26:55,736
But I can never satisfy you.

293
00:26:56,536 --> 00:26:59,136
You are trying to change me to be who you want me to be.

294
00:27:00,336 --> 00:27:02,336
I've done everything so that you'll be the most suitable one

295
00:27:02,337 --> 00:27:04,336
for the leader position of this family.

296
00:27:05,336 --> 00:27:06,136
Mom?

297
00:27:07,336 --> 00:27:11,136
If being me like this can't succeed the family, then I don’t want this.

298
00:27:11,536 --> 00:27:15,536
That's enough. Go to bed and forget about these nonsense things you said.

299
00:27:16,536 --> 00:27:18,636
You only care about what you want.

300
00:27:19,636 --> 00:27:22,136
You never care about me.

301
00:27:23,536 --> 00:27:25,336
You don't think I care?

302
00:27:25,436 --> 00:27:27,136
You want Yang to succeed everything

303
00:27:27,137 --> 00:27:28,736
instead of you?

304
00:27:29,136 --> 00:27:31,136
I did what I did because I love you.

305
00:27:31,336 --> 00:27:35,136
You don't love me, you only love yourself.

306
00:27:37,336 --> 00:27:39,136
You're worried that you would lose your power

307
00:27:40,136 --> 00:27:42,736
lose your powerful position in the family because you have a son like me.

308
00:27:42,936 --> 00:27:43,436
Ouch!

309
00:27:45,336 --> 00:27:47,536
Please stop.

310
00:27:47,736 --> 00:27:48,536
Tian.

311
00:27:50,536 --> 00:27:53,136
Don't tell me that I don't love you.

312
00:27:54,536 --> 00:27:57,736
You think I did all of this because I'm selfish?

313
00:27:59,536 --> 00:28:00,936
Think about it.

314
00:28:03,536 --> 00:28:05,736
How're you gonna live your life after this?

315
00:28:09,836 --> 00:28:10,736
Mom?

316
00:28:13,836 --> 00:28:16,536
I just want to live a happy life.

317
00:28:19,836 --> 00:28:25,736
You won't be happy as long as you continue to be like this.

318
00:28:55,936 --> 00:28:57,136
We got the tea!

319
00:28:57,137 --> 00:29:00,936
What's the tea? You didn't say anything earlier

320
00:29:00,937 --> 00:29:05,336
We've been watching them for 10 years and there's no progress.

321
00:29:05,337 --> 00:29:07,136
You've been watching them for 10 years

322
00:29:07,137 --> 00:29:09,136
and have you ever seen Li slapped her son?

323
00:29:09,736 --> 00:29:15,136
I think what made her slap her beloved son like that

324
00:29:15,736 --> 00:29:19,536
must be related to the thing they burned for sure.

325
00:29:20,136 --> 00:29:21,136
But what is it?

326
00:29:22,636 --> 00:29:25,136
Maybe it's not something serious.

327
00:29:25,336 --> 00:29:28,536
You slap Yang all the time.

328
00:29:28,936 --> 00:29:31,136
Hey! / Ouch!

329
00:29:31,336 --> 00:29:33,136
We're different.

330
00:29:34,936 --> 00:29:37,136
Didn't you hear Tian say that

331
00:29:37,336 --> 00:29:40,636
his mom would lose her power for having a son like him?

332
00:29:42,536 --> 00:29:45,936
Or Tian isn't her son?

333
00:29:46,536 --> 00:29:48,136
When he isn't her real son,

334
00:29:48,336 --> 00:29:51,136
she could lose her power.

335
00:29:52,136 --> 00:29:55,536
You heard people talking about other houses, didn't you? / Oops.

336
00:29:55,537 --> 00:29:56,736
That's so off the topic.

337
00:29:58,536 --> 00:30:01,136
I think what they're hiding must be big.

338
00:30:01,137 --> 00:30:03,536
Big enough to kick her out of her current position.

339
00:30:04,536 --> 00:30:06,536
I need to know what it is.

340
00:30:17,736 --> 00:30:21,536
You told me that you wanted to talk to me. What is it?

341
00:30:22,536 --> 00:30:23,936
About Tian.

342
00:30:24,536 --> 00:30:29,736
He's old enough to succeed everything in the family

343
00:30:30,836 --> 00:30:34,336
and you're working hard. You should rest already.

344
00:30:40,536 --> 00:30:42,536
Well, well

345
00:30:45,836 --> 00:30:49,536
you're rushing him to hand over his position to Tian like this,

346
00:30:50,536 --> 00:30:53,936
don't you think it's another way of rushing him to death?

347
00:30:55,336 --> 00:30:58,936
Who did that? I didn't say a word about dying.

348
00:30:59,136 --> 00:31:02,636
You don't have to. You want Tian to succeed Mr.Song,

349
00:31:03,136 --> 00:31:05,136
because you're afraid of something?

350
00:31:05,137 --> 00:31:08,536
I'm not afraid, I'm just…
That's enough. Stop.

351
00:31:11,836 --> 00:31:13,536
I've been thinking about this too.

352
00:31:14,636 --> 00:31:16,536
I want to rest already.

353
00:31:17,836 --> 00:31:21,136
I went to see when the good time is and it's only 6 months.

354
00:31:24,636 --> 00:31:26,536
But according to the custom,

355
00:31:26,636 --> 00:31:30,136
Tian needs to get married and has children to continue the family

356
00:31:30,636 --> 00:31:33,936
so I can trust that the business and Five Dragons Association

357
00:31:34,736 --> 00:31:36,536
would have a successor for sure.

358
00:31:38,536 --> 00:31:42,536
You can trust me about that. I'll find the most suitable person for Tian.

359
00:31:50,636 --> 00:31:53,136
Madame rushed Mr.Song to hand over his work to Tian already.

360
00:31:53,236 --> 00:31:55,636
She must be worried that what she was hiding could be unearthed.

361
00:31:56,136 --> 00:31:57,936
She's so smart.

362
00:31:57,937 --> 00:32:00,636
No wonder why she can keep a secret for 10 years.

363
00:32:02,136 --> 00:32:03,336
You want to work for her?

364
00:32:03,337 --> 00:32:07,136
She's too smart, she wouldn't want me to work for her.

365
00:32:07,536 --> 00:32:08,536
Ouch!

366
00:32:08,836 --> 00:32:10,536
You're picking at me many times already.

367
00:32:11,336 --> 00:32:12,336
I'm sorry.

368
00:32:14,836 --> 00:32:16,536
I can't wait any longer.

369
00:32:16,537 --> 00:32:19,536
I need to know the truth before Tian is succeeded.

370
00:32:19,736 --> 00:32:22,736
Otherwise, there's no more hope left for me.

371
00:32:27,736 --> 00:32:29,936
It'll be a performance at the temple today.

372
00:32:45,536 --> 00:32:46,136
Yang?

373
00:32:50,836 --> 00:32:53,536
What're you doing? Why didn't you use the door properly?

374
00:32:54,336 --> 00:32:55,736
Why didn't you get dressed?

375
00:32:56,136 --> 00:32:57,936
Get dressed? To where?

376
00:32:57,937 --> 00:32:59,136
To watch the Chinese opera performance.

377
00:33:01,336 --> 00:33:03,336
But dad told us not to go outside.

378
00:33:04,536 --> 00:33:05,936
I remembered that he forbid us

379
00:33:06,136 --> 00:33:09,536
so I climbed up here to sneak you out.

380
00:33:10,536 --> 00:33:14,736
What if he knew that we went outside? It'd be so bad.

381
00:33:16,136 --> 00:33:18,736
But I promised you to take you to watch it,

382
00:33:19,536 --> 00:33:22,136
you want me to break my own promise?

383
00:33:32,336 --> 00:33:34,336
Whoa!

384
00:33:35,836 --> 00:33:40,336
Save me a seat. I'll get some snacks and I'll follow you.

385
00:33:40,536 --> 00:33:41,536
Hurry up.

386
00:34:43,836 --> 00:34:44,736
Thank you.

387
00:34:52,536 --> 00:34:54,136
Why do you have to cover it up like that?

388
00:35:01,736 --> 00:35:06,136
This piece came from Chinese dynasty.

389
00:35:06,536 --> 00:35:11,136
It's not just valued in price but it's a sentimental piece.

390
00:35:11,536 --> 00:35:16,136
My family's memories are in here

391
00:35:18,336 --> 00:35:19,336
It's 100

392
00:35:19,536 --> 00:35:23,736
100? It's not even enough to buy gold.

393
00:35:24,536 --> 00:35:27,736
Take a look closely and carefully.

394
00:35:28,536 --> 00:35:30,936
It comes from China.

395
00:35:31,936 --> 00:35:37,936
I don't want to sell it. It's so valuable.

396
00:35:38,136 --> 00:35:41,336
If it's that valuable to you, then you should keep it.

397
00:35:43,136 --> 00:35:44,536
What should we do?

398
00:35:45,136 --> 00:35:46,136
Plan B.

399
00:35:48,136 --> 00:36:02,336
Please help me.

400
00:36:02,736 --> 00:36:06,736
My family is in a big trouble.

401
00:36:07,336 --> 00:36:11,336
Some days, I don't have anything to eat.

402
00:36:12,636 --> 00:36:14,736
Please help me.

403
00:36:19,136 --> 00:36:21,936
I'm so thirsty. I need water.

404
00:36:23,136 --> 00:36:26,936
Go buy him a drink. Come on.
Sure.

405
00:36:28,636 --> 00:36:34,136
Please wait a minute, she'll get you something to drink. / Sure.

406
00:36:34,336 --> 00:36:39,136
Actually, there's another way to earn money.

407
00:36:40,736 --> 00:36:42,136
Be my wife.

408
00:36:42,536 --> 00:36:43,136
Hey!

409
00:36:44,736 --> 00:36:48,136
Well, you need money? You can be my wife.

410
00:36:48,736 --> 00:36:50,136
Come on.

411
00:36:51,336 --> 00:36:52,336
Don't get any closer.

412
00:36:53,536 --> 00:36:55,136
Come to me, ouch!

413
00:36:56,336 --> 00:36:57,536
Don't!

414
00:36:58,936 --> 00:37:00,136
Don't run away from me.

415
00:37:04,636 --> 00:37:08,536
Ouch! / Argh!

416
00:38:11,936 --> 00:38:13,136
I'll get you a new one.

417
00:38:57,936 --> 00:38:58,836
Thank you.

418
00:40:04,782 --> 00:40:08,182
Noi! Run!

419
00:40:08,382 --> 00:40:09,782
Where to? / Ouch!

420
00:40:12,782 --> 00:40:13,782
Move!

421
00:40:14,782 --> 00:40:16,782
I'm sorry but please move.

422
00:40:19,182 --> 00:40:20,782
Where should we go?

423
00:40:22,782 --> 00:40:25,382
Noi!

424
00:40:28,782 --> 00:40:29,982
Stop!

425
00:41:02,382 --> 00:41:06,582
Did you see two women running here?

426
00:41:06,583 --> 00:41:09,582
She hit my head and ran away.

427
00:41:10,582 --> 00:41:13,782
I see.

428
00:41:15,282 --> 00:41:16,782
Women?

429
00:41:17,382 --> 00:41:18,782
That's right.

430
00:41:19,982 --> 00:41:23,782
What did they do to you?

431
00:41:23,982 --> 00:41:25,782
Why are you bleeding like that?

432
00:41:26,382 --> 00:41:30,282
I…I didn't do anything.

433
00:41:30,283 --> 00:41:32,182
They had something to sell.

434
00:41:32,382 --> 00:41:35,382
I offered her unmatched price so she was furious at me.

435
00:41:35,782 --> 00:41:39,082
Damn it! The fallen noble woman like her!

436
00:41:40,782 --> 00:41:43,782
What about this? You should call the police.

437
00:41:45,482 --> 00:41:49,782
If she did something wrong, you should go to the police.

438
00:41:50,182 --> 00:41:53,282
Nope. I feel bad for her.

439
00:41:54,182 --> 00:41:57,182
Is she hiding in a jar?

440
00:41:57,183 --> 00:42:00,982
What type of person would be hiding in a jar?

441
00:42:01,182 --> 00:42:03,382
A woman? With long hair? / That's right.

442
00:42:03,383 --> 00:42:05,182
I saw her running over there.

443
00:42:05,482 --> 00:42:06,182
Over there?

444
00:42:06,183 --> 00:42:07,782
That's right. You should follow her there.

445
00:42:07,783 --> 00:42:08,982
Sure. Thanks.

446
00:42:12,782 --> 00:42:13,782
Is he gone?

447
00:42:14,382 --> 00:42:16,782
What? I didn't quite hear you?

448
00:42:17,182 --> 00:42:18,782
Is he gone?

449
00:42:19,182 --> 00:42:21,782
Oh? That man?

450
00:42:21,982 --> 00:42:24,782
Yep? / Is he gone?

451
00:42:25,482 --> 00:42:27,082
Right? He's gone.

452
00:42:27,482 --> 00:42:30,182
Then you should get up already.

453
00:42:30,482 --> 00:42:32,182
Wait!

454
00:42:32,482 --> 00:42:33,982
Hey!

455
00:42:34,482 --> 00:42:39,082
Get up, now!

456
00:42:59,382 --> 00:43:01,782
Smells so bad.

457
00:43:02,782 --> 00:43:04,582
There're trashes in here.

458
00:43:05,782 --> 00:43:09,182
Let me ask you something, are you really a noble woman?

459
00:43:10,182 --> 00:43:10,782
Why?

460
00:43:11,182 --> 00:43:14,782
I've never seen a noble woman like you before.

461
00:43:15,782 --> 00:43:18,182
You can't possibly think that just because you helped me, you could say anything to me.

462
00:43:18,982 --> 00:43:21,582
You should see when I'm fully dressed. You'll be stunned.

463
00:43:25,282 --> 00:43:27,982
Thanks for helping me.

464
00:43:40,382 --> 00:43:46,382
I was born a Chinese, when I die, I want to be a Chinese ghost too.

465
00:43:46,383 --> 00:43:50,182
I'm ready to fight until my last blood to save my country.
Yang!

466
00:43:50,182 --> 00:43:59,382
I saw something really funny, I'll tell you later.
I don't care if I die.

467
00:43:59,383 --> 00:44:00,482
That's well said.

468
00:44:00,582 --> 00:44:02,582
I agreed.

469
00:44:07,182 --> 00:44:14,782
My name is Hua Mulan,

470
00:44:15,982 --> 00:44:24,982
and I've never betrayed my country.

471
00:44:25,482 --> 00:44:33,482
My determination is strong like a sun shining every day.
What did they say? What's the play?

472
00:44:33,482 --> 00:44:34,982
Mulanchi

473
00:44:35,482 --> 00:44:36,982
Mulanchi?

474
00:44:37,783 --> 00:44:46,382
After this meal, us, Chinese soldiers

475
00:44:46,982 --> 00:44:54,982
are ready to fight with Japanese soldiers so we'll know the result.

476
00:44:55,182 --> 00:44:56,582
Are you scared?

477
00:44:56,583 --> 00:44:57,782
Are you afraid of death?

478
00:44:57,783 --> 00:45:00,082
Nope!
Let's go home / Hey!

479
00:45:00,182 --> 00:45:01,782
We'll fight until we die
What is it?

480
00:45:01,783 --> 00:45:04,182
This is an adaptation to protest Japanese soldiers. / What?
Fight til we die!

481
00:45:04,182 --> 00:45:06,082
Let's go.

482
00:45:15,582 --> 00:45:18,782
Come on

483
00:45:18,783 --> 00:45:19,782
Mom? / Get out of the way.

484
00:45:19,783 --> 00:45:22,782
Come on, hide!

485
00:45:22,783 --> 00:45:25,782
You can go ahead, I'll follow you.

486
00:45:25,982 --> 00:45:26,982
Let's go.

487
00:45:27,182 --> 00:45:28,982
Mom? / Yang?

488
00:45:30,482 --> 00:45:30,982
Yang?

489
00:45:31,782 --> 00:45:37,982
Get up, kid! Come on. Are you okay?

490
00:45:38,182 --> 00:45:41,182
Let's find a place to hide.

491
00:45:47,482 --> 00:45:48,782
Hey!

492
00:45:56,482 --> 00:45:56,982
You!

493
00:46:01,482 --> 00:46:01,982
Let's go.

494
00:46:13,182 --> 00:46:14,782
Run! / Yang?

495
00:47:16,782 --> 00:47:18,982
Thank you.

496
00:47:21,982 --> 00:47:24,182
You're injured?

497
00:47:28,182 --> 00:47:28,782
Press it.

498
00:47:43,182 --> 00:47:44,782
Tian! / Yang!

499
00:47:46,182 --> 00:47:46,782
Come here.

500
00:48:10,782 --> 00:48:14,782
How much money have you got? I need to pay debt.

501
00:48:15,982 --> 00:48:18,982
There's an accident.

502
00:48:19,482 --> 00:48:21,382
The china was broken.

503
00:48:29,982 --> 00:48:36,182
It'd be better if you were born as a man, so you could be a government officer,

504
00:48:36,982 --> 00:48:39,782
or you could get more job options than this.

505
00:48:41,182 --> 00:48:44,782
Don't worry.

506
00:48:44,982 --> 00:48:48,982
Even though I'm a woman, I'll try to keep our palace

507
00:48:48,983 --> 00:48:50,782
so it won't be seized.

508
00:48:51,382 --> 00:48:55,582
Stop thinking about it. Let it be my job.

509
00:48:57,182 --> 00:48:59,282
You would? / Yes.

510
00:49:00,982 --> 00:49:06,182
You're so strong as one of noble family members.

511
00:49:13,482 --> 00:49:14,582
Come on.

512
00:49:17,782 --> 00:49:18,582
Come here.

513
00:49:19,782 --> 00:49:20,782
Slower.

514
00:49:25,482 --> 00:49:25,982
Let's go.

515
00:49:31,382 --> 00:49:33,782
How're you gonna go up there?

516
00:49:35,182 --> 00:49:37,782
You can step here and I'll push you up.

517
00:49:37,783 --> 00:49:39,782
Come on, we have no time to think.

518
00:49:39,882 --> 00:49:41,782
I'm gonna count to three.

519
00:49:41,783 --> 00:49:43,482
1..2..3…

520
00:49:43,483 --> 00:49:45,082
You're back? / Oops.

521
00:49:45,482 --> 00:49:46,282
Bua?

522
00:49:47,182 --> 00:49:51,182
I brought you something.

523
00:49:53,182 --> 00:49:57,182
Your dad waited to see both of you in the hallway.

524
00:50:09,482 --> 00:50:11,282
Yang and Tian are here.

525
00:50:16,282 --> 00:50:21,382
Someone saw both of you went out to watch the show, so they told me.

526
00:50:24,982 --> 00:50:25,782
Tian.

527
00:50:28,582 --> 00:50:31,182
Is that blood? Are you okay?

528
00:50:31,782 --> 00:50:32,982
I'm okay.

529
00:50:34,082 --> 00:50:36,182
It's the blood from someone who saved me. It's not mine.

530
00:50:37,382 --> 00:50:39,782
Good thing that it's somebody else's blood.

531
00:50:40,182 --> 00:50:42,382
If you keep on sneaking out like this,

532
00:50:43,282 --> 00:50:44,982
you will be the one bleeding for sure.

533
00:50:45,382 --> 00:50:48,582
I told you that during war time,

534
00:50:49,182 --> 00:50:50,782
don't just wander off like that.

535
00:50:51,182 --> 00:50:54,782
What if they were shooting? Aren't you scared?

536
00:50:55,382 --> 00:50:56,982
I…/ I'm sorry.

537
00:50:58,182 --> 00:51:00,782
I wanted to watch the show so I sneaked out.

538
00:51:03,382 --> 00:51:06,782
Because of you? You took Tian out?

539
00:51:07,182 --> 00:51:09,182
You watched a show about rebelling Japanese soldiers.

540
00:51:09,182 --> 00:51:11,182
What if they arrested you? What would you do?

541
00:51:12,782 --> 00:51:14,382
You'll ruin our family.

542
00:51:15,182 --> 00:51:16,582
You want to die?

543
00:51:16,583 --> 00:51:17,782
It's not like that.

544
00:51:17,783 --> 00:51:19,082
You need to calm down.

545
00:51:19,182 --> 00:51:22,582
You can't blame it all on Yang.

546
00:51:22,583 --> 00:51:25,782
Tian was there too. Tian was there,too.
Tian has nothing to do with this.

547
00:51:26,782 --> 00:51:27,282
Yang!

548
00:51:27,782 --> 00:51:31,782
I sneaked out. Tian knew about this so he came to get me.

549
00:51:31,982 --> 00:51:34,282
He was worried that I'd be punished.

550
00:51:35,782 --> 00:51:39,382
I warned you once and it didn't work.

551
00:51:40,182 --> 00:51:42,582
I thought I should punish you harder so you would remember.

552
00:51:43,382 --> 00:51:44,782
On your knees.

553
00:51:45,182 --> 00:51:47,482
Sir? / Sir?

554
00:51:51,482 --> 00:51:51,982
Yang!

555
00:51:55,482 --> 00:51:55,982
Yang!

556
00:52:03,182 --> 00:52:03,982
Tian!

557
00:52:06,482 --> 00:52:09,782
If you're gonna punish him, then you need to punish me too.

558
00:52:09,882 --> 00:52:11,782
What're you doing? Get up, now.

559
00:52:11,783 --> 00:52:14,182
Get up, now.

560
00:52:14,183 --> 00:52:15,782
Get up. / Get up.

561
00:52:15,783 --> 00:52:17,782
Get up, come here / Yang!

562
00:52:18,482 --> 00:52:18,982
Yang!

563
00:52:19,182 --> 00:52:22,782
You can't punish only Yang.

564
00:52:22,982 --> 00:52:26,182
It's not fair. You have to punish Tian too.

565
00:52:26,782 --> 00:52:29,782
It's my fault. I need to be punished.

566
00:52:31,582 --> 00:52:35,782
You're right. I shouldn't disobey you.

567
00:52:36,782 --> 00:52:39,082
There are lots of people died at the opera house.

568
00:52:39,982 --> 00:52:44,082
If I was shot or arrested,

569
00:52:44,482 --> 00:52:47,082
everyone here would be in trouble too.

570
00:52:47,482 --> 00:52:49,082
Please punish me.

571
00:52:49,482 --> 00:52:49,982
Yang!

572
00:52:53,482 --> 00:52:54,182
Yang! / Sir?

573
00:52:54,282 --> 00:52:55,782
Sir? / Yang!

574
00:52:56,182 --> 00:52:56,982
Dad!

575
00:52:57,182 --> 00:52:59,282
Don't do that. / Dad!

576
00:52:59,782 --> 00:53:00,782
Don't! / Stop!

577
00:53:00,783 --> 00:53:02,082
Don't hurt him.

578
00:53:02,182 --> 00:53:05,082
Sir? / Please don't hurt him.

579
00:53:05,482 --> 00:53:06,782
That's enough

580
00:53:06,783 --> 00:53:07,782
Please don't hurt him.

581
00:53:07,783 --> 00:53:11,782
Don't hurt him.

582
00:53:11,783 --> 00:53:13,782
That's enough / Please don't hurt him.

583
00:53:13,982 --> 00:53:15,982
That's enough.

584
00:53:16,482 --> 00:53:19,082
Stop!

585
00:53:19,482 --> 00:53:20,782
Don't hurt him / Tian?

586
00:53:20,783 --> 00:53:22,182
Get him upstairs.

587
00:53:22,183 --> 00:53:24,082
Don't hurt him.

588
00:53:24,982 --> 00:53:26,082
Don't hurt him.

589
00:53:27,182 --> 00:53:29,782
That's enough.

590
00:53:29,982 --> 00:53:32,782
Please don't hurt him.
Please stop.

591
00:53:32,783 --> 00:53:35,782
Sir? / He didn't listen to me.

592
00:53:35,882 --> 00:53:37,782
That's enough.

593
00:53:37,783 --> 00:53:39,282
It's enough / That's enough.

594
00:53:39,782 --> 00:53:41,782
It's enough / That's enough.

595
00:53:41,783 --> 00:53:42,782
That's enough.

596
00:53:42,982 --> 00:53:44,782
Yang is here safe and sound.

597
00:53:44,982 --> 00:53:47,782
He should learn his lesson by now.

598
00:53:50,782 --> 00:53:56,082
If you didn't learn your lesson, you'd die because of those Japanese soldiers.

599
00:54:04,382 --> 00:54:07,182
Sir?

600
00:54:07,183 --> 00:54:08,582
You're such..!

601
00:54:16,582 --> 00:54:18,582
Let me go.

602
00:54:18,782 --> 00:54:21,582
I told you to let me go!

603
00:54:22,382 --> 00:54:24,782
Let me go. / Ouch!

604
00:54:24,783 --> 00:54:25,982
Stop right now!

605
00:54:37,782 --> 00:54:41,282
You want your dad to know that you were the one who wanted to watch the show, not Yang?

606
00:54:41,582 --> 00:54:44,782
You knew that I was the one wanted to go.

607
00:54:45,182 --> 00:54:46,982
Why didn't you tell dad

608
00:54:47,282 --> 00:54:48,782
that I made a mistake?

609
00:54:49,782 --> 00:54:51,182
Or you're worried that he would be mad?

610
00:54:51,183 --> 00:54:52,982
And he wouldn't hand over his work to me?

611
00:54:53,782 --> 00:54:55,782
And you wouldn't be a female leader of this house anymore.

612
00:54:57,382 --> 00:54:59,982
That's right. I'm worried that I would lose my power.

613
00:54:59,983 --> 00:55:02,782
I don't care about you. I don't love you at all.

614
00:55:02,982 --> 00:55:04,982
If you had been shot by Japanese soldiers,

615
00:55:04,983 --> 00:55:07,782
I would have lost my position as the head of the house as well.

616
00:55:08,582 --> 00:55:12,382
If I was shot to death, it would be better, right?

617
00:55:12,582 --> 00:55:14,182
Better than letting someone know who I am.

618
00:55:15,382 --> 00:55:18,782
Please don't be sarcastic to one another like that.

619
00:55:24,182 --> 00:55:26,782
No matter how hard you tried to accuse me of being selfish,

620
00:55:27,982 --> 00:55:31,782
I'll try to hide everyone about who you are.

621
00:56:19,182 --> 00:56:22,182
Please be gentle, it hurts.

622
00:56:22,382 --> 00:56:26,182
I'd like to slap more of you. Why would you protect him like that?

623
00:56:26,782 --> 00:56:30,182
You should have used this chance for your dad to scold him.

624
00:56:30,582 --> 00:56:32,782
So your dad would take him down from being the first successor.

625
00:56:32,783 --> 00:56:34,082
And you can be the first one instead.

626
00:56:34,182 --> 00:56:35,582
Be gentle.

627
00:56:36,182 --> 00:56:39,582
It's not that easy.

628
00:56:40,782 --> 00:56:42,582
When you two went out together,

629
00:56:42,782 --> 00:56:46,582
you should have sent him to Japanese soldiers so they would have ended him.

630
00:56:47,282 --> 00:56:49,982
Can you stop pushing me to be a bad guy?

631
00:56:50,382 --> 00:56:53,782
I've heard you told me this since I was young.

632
00:56:53,982 --> 00:56:55,782
I told you already

633
00:56:55,783 --> 00:56:58,782
I won't fight with Tian for any position, no matter what.

634
00:57:00,182 --> 00:57:02,182
You can call me mean or whatever.

635
00:57:02,482 --> 00:57:05,182
But I did all of these for you

636
00:57:06,182 --> 00:57:09,582
A mother wants the best for her son and I…

637
00:57:10,982 --> 00:57:13,382
I…I don't want

638
00:57:13,582 --> 00:57:16,582
to see you being pushed to the ground like I did my whole life.

639
00:57:18,382 --> 00:57:19,382
Listen to me.

640
00:57:20,182 --> 00:57:23,782
If we're in our place, Madame won't mess with us.

641
00:57:23,982 --> 00:57:25,582
No, you listen to me.

642
00:57:26,782 --> 00:57:28,782
You're one of your dad's sons.

643
00:57:29,182 --> 00:57:31,982
You have a right to own everything that belongs to you

644
00:57:31,983 --> 00:57:33,582
as much as Tian.

645
00:57:33,583 --> 00:57:35,982
But everything belongs to Tian since the beginning.

646
00:57:35,983 --> 00:57:39,982
How did you know? If Tian really is the most suitable one,

647
00:57:41,982 --> 00:57:45,382
then what is his secret that his mom tried to hide? What is that?

648
00:57:46,982 --> 00:57:48,782
You should leave him alone.

649
00:57:53,982 --> 00:57:54,782
Yang!

650
00:57:56,782 --> 00:57:58,782
What if something that they hide

651
00:58:00,982 --> 00:58:04,282
is really bad and it could ruin our family?

652
00:58:05,782 --> 00:58:06,782
What'd you do?

653
00:58:11,182 --> 00:58:12,782
I'll stand by Tian.

654
00:58:13,482 --> 00:58:17,782
I'll support Tian and encourage him to solve the family's problem.

655
00:58:19,182 --> 00:58:19,982
Ouch!

656
00:58:41,982 --> 00:58:44,182
Am I too selfish?

657
00:58:44,382 --> 00:58:46,382
Am I the bad mother?

658
00:58:46,383 --> 00:58:47,382
Madame.

659
00:58:47,782 --> 00:58:50,582
No matter what I do, Tian will be disagreeing with me.

660
00:58:50,583 --> 00:58:53,182
He thinks that I did all of these for myself.

661
00:58:53,183 --> 00:58:56,782
When I did all of these for him.

662
00:58:56,982 --> 00:59:02,182
Tian hasn’t been old enough to know the world like you did.

663
00:59:02,982 --> 00:59:06,382
He will understand that you did all of these

664
00:59:06,582 --> 00:59:08,782
because you love and care for him.

665
00:59:47,582 --> 00:59:50,182
Tian? Madame wanted to see you.

666
01:00:03,182 --> 01:00:04,182
Tian's here.

667
01:00:08,182 --> 01:00:10,582
This is Pat.

668
01:00:12,182 --> 01:00:12,782
Hello.

669
01:00:13,182 --> 01:00:13,782
Hello.

670
01:00:15,382 --> 01:00:17,382
And that's Pin.

671
01:00:20,182 --> 01:00:21,782
Hello, Tian.

672
01:00:21,782 --> 01:00:23,782
Hello.

673
01:00:32,182 --> 01:00:33,982
Do you remember her?

674
01:00:34,182 --> 01:00:36,582
She used to play at our house.

675
01:00:37,982 --> 01:00:38,982
I didn't.

676
01:00:43,382 --> 01:00:48,782
Well, I didn't quite remember about it either.

677
01:00:49,982 --> 01:00:55,782
That's true. Well, you will start to remember something when you two start chatting.

678
01:00:56,982 --> 01:01:01,182
Pin just came back from oversea.

679
01:01:01,582 --> 01:01:05,382
She must have a lot of fun stories to tell you.

680
01:01:08,982 --> 01:01:12,182
Why don't you take her to the garden?

681
01:01:12,183 --> 01:01:13,782
The adults will discuss something here.

682
01:01:16,982 --> 01:01:18,182
Sure.

683
01:01:27,782 --> 01:01:29,782
My tummy hurts.

684
01:01:31,182 --> 01:01:32,482
Are you okay?

685
01:01:32,782 --> 01:01:33,782
I need to use the bathroom.

686
01:01:33,982 --> 01:01:34,982
You should go.

687
01:01:41,382 --> 01:01:44,182
The weather is nice today.

688
01:01:45,182 --> 01:01:45,682
Yeah.

689
01:01:48,182 --> 01:01:50,582
Your garden is pretty.

690
01:01:53,182 --> 01:01:54,582
Yeah.

691
01:02:05,982 --> 01:02:08,782
I think we should sit down.

692
01:02:10,482 --> 01:02:10,982
Okay.

693
01:02:17,782 --> 01:02:19,782
Ouch!

694
01:02:32,782 --> 01:02:33,982
You!

695
01:02:40,782 --> 01:02:42,782
You know her?

696
01:02:43,382 --> 01:02:44,182
That night…

697
01:02:44,183 --> 01:02:48,982
No, I didn't. Maybe he is mistaking me with someone.

698
01:02:54,782 --> 01:02:55,382
Tian.

699
01:02:55,582 --> 01:02:58,782
There's a problem about accounting at the warehouse, can you please check?

700
01:02:59,582 --> 01:03:00,782
Sure, I'll follow you.

701
01:03:04,982 --> 01:03:08,182
Can you chat with her? I need to go see something.

702
01:03:10,182 --> 01:03:10,782
Tian!

703
01:03:20,582 --> 01:03:22,582
We've never met?

704
01:03:23,182 --> 01:03:23,982
Nope.

705
01:03:24,582 --> 01:03:26,982
But I think we have.

706
01:03:27,782 --> 01:03:30,782
You must be mistaking me with someone. It was dark at the temple.

707
01:03:30,982 --> 01:03:34,182
And it was late. Your eyes couldn't be worked properly.

708
01:03:35,182 --> 01:03:35,982
Excuse me.

709
01:03:38,382 --> 01:03:40,782
Did I tell you that we met at the temple?

710
01:03:42,382 --> 01:03:45,582
Did I tell you that we met at night?

711
01:03:46,582 --> 01:03:51,782
I was just guessing. I'm good at guessing.

712
01:03:51,982 --> 01:03:54,982
And many people said that

713
01:03:54,983 --> 01:03:57,182
they saw someone who looked like me at the temple all the time.

714
01:04:02,182 --> 01:04:04,782
But I'm sure that I saw you. I wasn't wrong about this.

715
01:04:05,982 --> 01:04:09,982
You wanted it to be me?

716
01:04:12,182 --> 01:04:15,582
Supposed that I was there

717
01:04:15,982 --> 01:04:18,782
then it was just a little misunderstanding.

718
01:04:19,182 --> 01:04:20,782
A gentleman like you

719
01:04:20,982 --> 01:04:24,782
won't talk about the lady behind her back, right?

720
01:04:25,182 --> 01:04:26,782
I need to think about it.

721
01:04:27,182 --> 01:04:31,182
Because the woman that I met that night wasn't exactly a lady.

722
01:04:31,382 --> 01:04:33,382
She was more like an untamed mare.

723
01:04:35,182 --> 01:04:39,782
I could forget what happened that night if I was in a good mood.

724
01:04:41,182 --> 01:04:42,982
But don't make me mad,

725
01:04:43,982 --> 01:04:48,182
or I could say something.

726
01:05:05,182 --> 01:05:08,382
How's today? Isn't Pin cute or what?

727
01:05:12,182 --> 01:05:14,982
Please don't do this. I feel awkward.

728
01:05:16,182 --> 01:05:19,182
You seem to be awkward and uncomfortable in everything I wanted you to do.

729
01:05:19,582 --> 01:05:21,582
You know what it is.

730
01:05:22,582 --> 01:05:24,582
Please don't force me.

731
01:05:25,782 --> 01:05:29,182
I just wanted you two to know each other. Why do you have to go against me on this?

732
01:05:29,782 --> 01:05:35,382
Pin is a good girl and she's cute. You should get to know her and everything will be better.

733
01:05:44,182 --> 01:05:46,182
Madame is a witch.

734
01:05:46,382 --> 01:05:49,282
When Mr.Song said that her son needs to get married before become a successor.

735
01:05:49,582 --> 01:05:52,982
She's eager to find a woman for her son.

736
01:05:52,983 --> 01:05:55,782
If I was her, I would be in a hurry as well.

737
01:05:56,982 --> 01:05:59,782
She invited Pin, a daughter of Pat here.

738
01:05:59,982 --> 01:06:03,582
I heard that they have nothing left but their family name.

739
01:06:03,782 --> 01:06:06,982
Otherwise, he wouldn't put his palace in mortgage with Madame.

740
01:06:08,582 --> 01:06:10,782
He would give her daughter as a way to pay for interest.

741
01:06:10,882 --> 01:06:14,182
Just like when your dad gave you to Mr.Song,

742
01:06:14,282 --> 01:06:15,782
to pay debt.

743
01:06:15,982 --> 01:06:18,782
I would have slapped their mouth if you were someone else.

744
01:06:18,982 --> 01:06:22,082
But you said it so I would kick you instead.

745
01:06:22,182 --> 01:06:24,282
I'm sorry.

746
01:06:28,182 --> 01:06:31,182
Song Family is wealthy.

747
01:06:31,782 --> 01:06:34,382
But the family name is not that noble.

748
01:06:34,782 --> 01:06:37,782
She prefers Pin because of this.

749
01:06:37,982 --> 01:06:40,782
That's right, they only got their noble name

750
01:06:40,982 --> 01:06:43,582
if Tian got married with Pin,

751
01:06:43,583 --> 01:06:46,782
they would be a perfect couple.

752
01:06:49,182 --> 01:06:49,982
You're right about this.

753
01:06:51,782 --> 01:06:55,282
But I need to get in their way.

754
01:06:57,982 --> 01:07:00,982
You want to mess with their wedding, and you want to know about the secret.

755
01:07:01,182 --> 01:07:03,382
Will you be success in any of this?

756
01:07:14,182 --> 01:07:17,182
Are you sneaking into Tian's bedroom?

757
01:07:17,183 --> 01:07:19,182
Aren't you afraid that you would get caught?

758
01:07:19,782 --> 01:07:24,582
Nope. Because you're one to get inside, not me.

759
01:07:26,182 --> 01:07:29,582
Go inside and search. So we'd know what they're hiding.

760
01:07:32,382 --> 01:07:35,782
My tummy hurts, I need to use the bathroom.

761
01:07:35,783 --> 01:07:36,283
Wait!

762
01:08:12,982 --> 01:08:14,282
What the hell is he hiding?

763
01:08:53,582 --> 01:08:54,582
What the hell?

764
01:08:56,982 --> 01:08:58,782
He's preparing this for Pin?

765
01:09:08,782 --> 01:09:11,582
Please holy spirit, help me.

766
01:09:11,782 --> 01:09:16,782
If Tian was hiding something, please let me find it.

767
01:09:25,482 --> 01:09:26,182
Tian!

768
01:09:27,982 --> 01:09:30,982
Where're you going? Stop, now.

769
01:09:31,482 --> 01:09:32,182
Tian!

770
01:09:35,782 --> 01:09:38,182
I told you to stop by to see Pin at her house, why didn't you?

771
01:09:41,382 --> 01:09:42,182
I don't want to.

772
01:09:42,382 --> 01:09:43,782
You have to go, even if you didn't want to.

773
01:09:44,182 --> 01:09:45,982
You met her once.

774
01:09:45,983 --> 01:09:47,782
Don't be too quick to judge her.

775
01:09:47,783 --> 01:09:51,582
I didn't judge her. I don't care if she's a nice girl,

776
01:09:51,782 --> 01:09:53,782
she's not the right one for me.

777
01:09:54,982 --> 01:09:57,782
I chose her for you, of course she's the right one.

778
01:09:59,182 --> 01:10:01,482
You should come to say hi to her so she'd be happy.

779
01:10:01,782 --> 01:10:04,182
Bring her something. I prepared it for you.

780
01:10:04,382 --> 01:10:06,582
You're pushing me too much.

781
01:10:06,583 --> 01:10:09,782
If I didn't push you, someone would know about you already.

782
01:10:11,482 --> 01:10:14,782
Maybe I want people to know about me.

783
01:10:51,982 --> 01:10:53,182
What's going on?

784
01:11:30,782 --> 01:11:32,782
We find the right time for you.

785
01:11:32,783 --> 01:11:33,782
The right time to get married.

786
01:11:33,982 --> 01:11:35,582
The family's pin.

787
01:11:35,583 --> 01:11:37,182
Please, don't

788
01:11:37,183 --> 01:11:39,782
I'll do anything for my son.

789
01:11:41,982 --> 01:11:44,182
